title: derma e Firming Moisturizer, DMAE- Alpha Lipoic - C-Ester, 2 oz (56 g) (Pack of 2)
description: Widely-acclaimed DMAE and alpha Lipoic Acid are combined with C-Ester in this rich moisturizing formula that both hydrates your skin and improves its elasticity. Please note: Contains 1% of alpha Lipoic acid. May cause tingling when applied. No animal testing. Made in USA.

title: MyChelle Fruit Fiesta Peel, 1.2-Ounce Jar
description: Antioxidant and nutrient dense organic raspberry puree, and natural acids romance your skin to a more radiant, youthful glow.  You will feel a light tingling and stimulating effect that will leave your skin refreshed.  This peel is not for beginners, patch test before using all over.

title: MyChelle Deep Repair Cream, 1.2-Ounce Jar
description: Deep Repair Cream is an advanced nourishing cream providing exceptional extracts to improve and maintain moisture balance and radiance.  Venucean™, is from the deep sea of the Gulf of California, is rich in antioxidants and strengthens the skin’s resistance against aggression such as UV light.  Kambuchka™, is a black tea ferment that improves the skin’s quality and smoothness. Epidermal Growth Factor (EGF) assists skin healing and cellular repair.
